## Decisions Made
- Pin knowledge-distillery checkout to immutable commit SHA instead of moving main ref: prevents supply-chain attack vector where contents:write grants arbitrary code execution to whatever is on main
- Make _replay() read WAL file as source-of-truth instead of stdin: stdin payload could diverge from the WAL, losing pending recovery state during crash recovery
- Dismiss CodeRabbit finding on tests/all.sh plugin.json find predicate: verified the file is at plugins/agent-atelier/.claude-plugin/plugin.json, so the -path "*/.claude-plugin/*" filter is correct

## Problems Encountered
